---
title: Moroccan-Spiced Bean Bowl with Couscous and Feta
description: This delicious bean bowl is packed with amazing moroccan flavours like, citrusy lemon and salty feta! Red onions, orange bell peppers and spinach are just a few veggies that make up this colourful and tasty dish!
